@Lee adding a summary of our call here for everybody's reference.
There is a known exception with the Converse APIs, *all the conversations created by APIs are incompatible with the UI and vice versa* i.e. any conversations created by the APIs should only be operated on by the APIs, and same applies for conversations created by the UI (both conversations are hidden from the others list as well)
cc @Balaram @Varun Jain
